For 45 years, DPACI has provided EEE parts solutions towards improving reliability and
combatting obsolescence in the American defense and space industry. We perform counterfeit
analysis to ISO17025/AS6171, up screen commercially available electronic components to
MIL-STD-883/750/202 military standards, manufacture custom packaging per MIL-PRF-38535,
extract die from certified PEMs and semiconductor devices, and repackage devices into ceramic
fixtures that can satisfy form, fit, and function requirements for military and space components.
